   He's come so far, so fast that all over this country of ours
people are asking questions: What kind of man is he, what kind of
governor has he been, what kind of president will he be.
   He's been my friend a long time.
   And I'd like to tell you my answers to those questions. I'd also
like to tell you why I believe Michael Dukakis should be the first
American president born of immigrant parents since Andrew Jackson.
</TEXT>
