message that gave honor to us all. He told us his name would be
placed in nomination tonight for the presidency of the United
States of America.
   He also said, when he is nominated, you all are nominated.
   Tonight, I'm proud to second the nomination of Jesse Louis
Jackson and, in doing so, we're all indeed nominated. My mother and
my twelve brothers and sisters are proud tonight. My mother knows
